Author: rexie7
Text: i hate that tumblr does this. ive had five accounts terminated in the past six months. smfh.  it doesnt even do shit as deleting accounts doesnt delete things you've posted that others have reblogged, so wtf is the point of deleting accounts if ed shit is always gonna be out there?   and its not like we're not gonna make another account so what is it even accomplishing???
